---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Prose from '../components/Prose.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - My Blog" description="Learn more about this blog and its author">
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-peach-cream py-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-soft-white rounded-lg shadow-sm p-8 md:p-12">
        <Prose>
          <h1>About This Blog</h1>
          
          <p>Welcome to my personal blog, a space where I share thoughts, insights, and stories from my journey in technology, life, and everything in between.</p>
          
          <h2>What You'll Find Here</h2>
          
          <p>This blog covers a variety of topics including:</p>
          
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Technology & Programming</strong> - Web development, software engineering, and the latest in tech</li>
            <li><strong>Personal Reflections</strong> - Life lessons, experiences, and thoughts on various topics</li>
            <li><strong>Projects & Tutorials</strong> - Step-by-step guides and project showcases</li>
            <li><strong>Industry Insights</strong> - Observations about the tech industry and its evolution</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2>About the Author</h2>
          
          <p>I'm passionate about creating meaningful digital experiences and sharing knowledge with others. When I'm not coding or writing, you can find me exploring new technologies, reading, or enjoying the outdoors.</p>
          
          <p>I believe in the power of community-driven learning and the importance of documenting our journeys. This blog serves as both a personal archive and a resource for others who might find value in these shared experiences.</p>
          
          <h2>Technical Details</h2>
          
          <p>This blog is built with modern web technologies:</p>
          
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Astro</strong> - For fast, static site generation</li>
            <li><strong>MDX</strong> - For rich content with interactive components</li>
            <li><strong>Tailwind CSS</strong> - For beautiful, responsive styling</li>
            <li><strong>Decap CMS</strong> - For easy content management</li>
          </ul>
          
          <p>The site features accessible footnote popovers, clean typography, and a mobile-first design approach.</p>
          
          <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
          
          <p>I'd love to hear from you! Whether you have questions about a post, suggestions for future content, or just want to say hello, feel free to reach out.</p>
          
          <p>Thank you for visiting, and I hope you find something valuable here!</p>
        </Prose>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
